9-08-02T05:05:38.000Z","msg":"公司應該得一兩個罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb955c2a2989f99cc8518c9c57482e6513bde819","tid":1396250,"uid":277114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:06:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef1795c76812ff353d3c7af5f9907291762a5e05","tid":1396250,"uid":224894,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"成間鋪都話罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c35493784bf52de3d0133986747d1a1413bbbb4","tid":1396250,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">我地可以迫大集團表態，<br />\n只要佢地肯表態唔反對，<br />\n市民自然會少左個包袱去罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一人一信 推到 大貓 今日內交代 8月5罷工 立場！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1396162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1396162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AMiNLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AMiNLW.jpg&h=611f7a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Email template: </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">可以開個新email send俾自己老細</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSubject <br />\nPlease ensure the safety of our staff on 5th August Strike<br />\n<br />\nContent <br />\nDear Management of ___________,  <br />\n<br />\nAccording to sources as diverse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=99111413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"a1468e8dc8e2681e7a290c4b66c04b556bbadc21","tid":1396250,"uid":61431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"我個dept廿幾個人，暫時得我一個罷<br />\n<br />\n唔撚驚，假已拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a2cee7b953ef162fd82c7418df70bb2251bb80","tid":1396250,"uid":267942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"我都罷工"},{"pid":"7495a078bcac488390b932e440c02686495c2734","tid":1396250,"uid":265954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"我成問公司5號都off 老細主動話星期一休息。<br />\n利申，觀塘細公司50人左右"},{"pid":"4eb3fddcd36f788aca623c6bfb069bbf9a02505e","tid":1396250,"uid":265954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7495a078bcac488390b932e440c02686495c2734","tid":1396250,"uid":265954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"我成問公司5號都off 老細主動話星期一休息。<br />\n利申，觀塘細公司50人左右"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-